      <p>
        Your e-mail address will be used by the Dirtybird as with any general participant email. As an opt-in participant your email address will also be provided to third parties to provide you information about music industry related opportunities. This includes job opportunities, contracts, sub-contracts, products and services offered by associated comapnies & third parties.
