        <li>Other game making contests, press, journalists or allied communities within the Global Game Jam® community network for the - purpose of announcing, recruiting, advertising and applauding efforts of GGJ participants.</li>
        <li>The organization reserves the right to provide these emails to third parties when explicit consent is provided by the participant.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>2. How pricing & Payment </h3>
      <p>
        Fees are collected via credit card on a recurring basis. Members can cancel at any time, and any content they receive during membership is theirs to keep for their personal use forever.
